    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_4f5aecd5">
            <lb /><orgName corresp="welte.studios">The Welte-Mignon Studios</orgName>
            <lb />667 Fifth Avenue-at 53rd Street
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b669256d">
            <lb />A really satisfactory way
            <lb />to buy musical instruments</div>
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_cd8eef02">
            <lb /><hi rend="#i">A</hi> FEELING of utter confidence is engendered at the
            <lb /><orgName corresp="welte.studios">Welte Mignon Studios</orgName>. You
            instinctively know
            <lb />that your continued patronage is sought and, therefore,
            <lb />that
            everything will be made to bend toward
            <lb />giving you thorough and complete
            <lb />satisfaction.
            There is a wide range of
            <lb />instruments from which to choose, at
            <lb />prices and on
            terms thoroughly in
            <lb />accord with your own idea of what is
            <lb />equitable.</div>
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_6dcfb305">
            <lb />The Welte-Mignon
            <lb />Reproducing Piano
            <lb />The instrument chosen by
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/124379923">Lhe-<lb/>vinne</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">
                <sic>Hofman</sic>
            </persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118518011">Busoni</persName>
            <lb />and scores of others, to
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                preserve their genius for posterity.
            </seg>
            <lb />You should hear <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski's</persName> reproductions;
            <seg ana="#soul_imprint" resp="#np" type="topic">
                hear how
                <lb />he has played
                his soul into indestructible records for the
                <lb /><orgName corresp="welte.studios">Welte-Mignon</orgName>
            </seg>.
            <seg ana="#repeatability" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Records which you may
                reproduce at any
                <lb />time and as often as you like
            </seg>, in your own home.
            <lb />One hundred
            and fifty-six musicians have recorded more
            <lb />than five thousand selections for the <orgName corresp="welte.studios">Welte-Mignon</orgName>. Imagine
            <lb />the delight to be derived from such a collection.
            <seg ana="#affordability">
                And consider
                <lb />that the Welte-Mignon Reproducing Piano is within
                <lb />everyone's means, for it may be
                bought on your terms, with
                <lb />in reason.
            </seg>
            <lb />Just drop in at the Studios to hear the
            Welte play. Please
            <lb />feel free to ask for your favorite selections. We consider the
            <lb />pleasure
            entirely ours.
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_8162a045">
